  <body id="page-top">
    <header class="masthead">
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="header-content-inner">
          <h1 id="homeHeading">Welcome to Elang</h1>
          <hr>
          <p> Practice a language and share experiences.
          </p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary btn-xl js-scroll-trigger" href="#about">Find Out More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="bg-primary" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <!-- <div class="row"> -->
          <div class="col-lg-8 mx-auto text-center">
            </p>
            <h2 class="section-heading text-white">Here you can connect entertainment to language!</h2>
            <hr class="light">
            <p class="text-faded">  
                                    There are many researches on the elderly person living in nursing homes getting sad due to the lack of family visits.
                                    Even if some elderly people live with her/his family, we know how difficult is giving attention to them given that
                                    the families are busy most of the times.
                                    All of us need to have a good conversation sometimes. And they have a lot to tell!
                                  
            <p class="text-faded">                       
                                    Why not exercise your skills in a language with an elderly person's knowledgement?
                                    Exercise what you learned and improve your conversation skills!
                                    In addition, you can make a difference.
            </p>
            <p class="text-faded">                        
                                    Our purpose is to connect people who have a lot to teach to those who want to learn.
                                    You can start a conversation with one of them now!
            </p>
            <% if !user_signed_in? %>
              <%= link_to "Sign Up", new_user_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-xl btn-default"%>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        <!--</div>-->
      </div>
    </section>
